title._content: Ciao Italia: Taste of Italy - October 25, 2018

description._content: A wonderful evening was had by all October 25, 2018 at the NHPBS Ciao Italia: Taste of Italy benefit to celebrate the launch of Mary Ann Esposito's new cookbook; Caio Italia My Lifelong Food Adventures in Italy. This special evening held at Tuscan Kitchen in Portsmouth began with a VIP guest tour around the Tuscan Marketplace and flowed into an incredibly delicious authentically Italian 3 course meal in the Tuscan dining room with recipes from Mary Ann's new cookbook. On hand was wine expert and the always entertaining, Joe Comforti to pair and explain special wines chosen especially for this event.  Thank you all who joined us.
